Description: The asciiConverter package provides users with a creative and simple
 way to convert regular text into fun ASCII art text that is bolded and block styled.
 Users can input text through various sources, and the package outputs stylized block
 text either to the R console or to files. This package aims to offer a visually
 appealing and versatile tool that is easy to use, allowing users to customize output
 for messages, headers, or other creative purposes.
